Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.96,0:01:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月夜的暗殺者
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.18,0:01:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.98,0:02:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.09,0:02:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們來遲一步嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.33,0:02:12.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那幾個傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.17,0:02:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.94,0:02:29.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.74,0:02:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.51,0:02:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一定是太勉強自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.98,0:02:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像那時一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.55,0:02:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.19,0:02:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡卡西老師明明說不用擔心傷痕了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.79,0:02:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙是誰啊 小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.10,0:02:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.00,0:02:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.13,0:02:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙到底是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.77,0:02:58.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然他的外貌改變了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.54,0:03:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過他就是那個我愛羅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.48,0:03:07.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一生下來就害死了\N那個本該稱為母親的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.12,0:03:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓我變成最強的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.45,0:03:15.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親用忍術讓砂的化身附在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.46,0:03:19.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我生下來就是個怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.53,0:03:22.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是他說的怪物嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.60,0:03:26.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個傢伙將佐助…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.27,0:03:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.34,0:03:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下並不是戰鬥忍犬 所以就不參戰了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.74,0:03:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事看到你的時候就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.94,0:03:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 趕快離開這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.11,0:03:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再設法將佐助帶到卡卡西老師那裡去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.65,0:03:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.46,0:03:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.16,0:03:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的你最多只能使用兩次
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.80,0:03:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.16,0:03:58.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別想發動第三次
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.17,0:04:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要牢記
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.34,0:04:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你強行發動這個術
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.67,0:04:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不但無法成功 還會耗光所有查克拉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.61,0:04:12.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好還會因此喪命
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.55,0:04:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你幸運地活了下來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.12,0:04:23.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對你而言也不是什麼好結果
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.63,0:04:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別是你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.50,0:04:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是咒印嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.24,0:04:39.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果因為你過於憎恨想依賴咒印的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.74,0:04:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的成長就會停滯不前
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.24,0:04:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣你就無法打贏鼬了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.58,0:04:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得想辦法克制住它
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.76,0:04:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.76,0:04:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 你就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.96,0:05:01.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時我沒殺的那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.10,0:05:07.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只為自己而戰 只愛自己而活
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.77,0:05:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我該殺的人還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.17,0:05:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的存在就不會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.98,0:05:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.43,0:05:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧 宇智波佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.00,0:05:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.88,0:05:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快滾開
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.60,0:06:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.47,0:06:17.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她居然敢挺身擋在我愛羅的面前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.91,0:06:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.34,0:06:23.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在該怎麼辦才好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.75,0:06:28.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想和這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.42,0:06:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 讓我感受一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.26,0:06:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.20,0:06:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛羅少爺 請您冷靜下來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.39,0:07:09.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.73,0:07:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙子會妨礙我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.96,0:07:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛羅少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.36,0:07:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜叉丸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.60,0:07:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別看我這麼虛弱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.52,0:07:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風影大人特別安排我以醫療班的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.39,0:07:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照顧您並時刻保護您
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.47,0:07:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請您不要在我面前做這樣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.98,0:07:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說砂子會自動保護您
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.42,0:07:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜叉丸 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.42,0:07:45.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是一點皮肉傷而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.43,0:07:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受傷會很痛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.27,0:07:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一點痛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.00,0:07:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過很快就會好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.45,0:08:07.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 夜叉丸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.95,0:08:09.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.72,0:08:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛是什麼感覺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.02,0:08:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我從小到大都沒受過傷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.16,0:08:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道那是什麼感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.53,0:08:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這該怎麼形容呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.60,0:08:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是痛苦 還是難過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.67,0:08:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.64,0:08:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被別人弄傷以致無法忍受
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.81,0:08:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法保持正常狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.68,0:08:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不太會形容
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.28,0:08:46.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之就是一種不太好的狀態啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.03,0:09:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜叉丸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.54,0:09:08.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜叉丸是不是…也討厭我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.85,0:09:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人活著多少都會傷害別人或被別人傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.76,0:09:28.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是人不會輕易去討厭一個人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.50,0:09:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 夜叉丸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.34,0:09:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想我大概明白痛的感覺了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.77,0:09:38.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.28,0:09:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我是不是和大家一樣 也受傷了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.38,0:09:49.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我常常覺得好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.72,0:09:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然沒有流血 但是覺得這裡好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.81,0:10:22.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體受傷時會流血 看起來很痛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.05,0:10:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是隨著時間流逝 疼痛會自然消失
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.62,0:10:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果用藥物治療就會好得更快
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.76,0:10:33.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過心裡創傷就比較麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.79,0:10:36.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼比心痛更難治癒的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.16,0:10:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心裡創傷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.93,0:10:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體受傷和心裡受傷有點不同
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.17,0:10:46.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心裡創傷無藥可治
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.67,0:10:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至一輩子都無法痊癒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.05,0:10:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.59,0:10:59.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一種東西可以治癒心裡創傷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.66,0:11:04.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這種藥方不容易找
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.19,0:11:06.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能從別人那裡獲得
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.79,0:11:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.80,0:11:09.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼做才能…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.10,0:11:13.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以治療心裡創傷的就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.17,0:11:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.01,0:11:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.61,0:11:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.71,0:11:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我該怎麼做才能得到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.08,0:11:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要怎麼做才能治癒這種疼痛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.88,0:11:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛羅少爺其實早就得到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.46,0:11:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂的愛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.76,0:11:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是為身邊最重要的人奉獻犧牲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.33,0:11:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以慈悲的心保護他的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.40,0:11:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像姐姐一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.50,0:11:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得姐姐一直很疼我愛羅少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.40,0:11:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砂之守鶴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.01,0:11:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來就是為了攻擊而存在的生靈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.71,0:11:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砂會自動保護我愛羅少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.21,0:12:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像是母親的愛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.72,0:12:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得您身邊的這些砂子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.65,0:12:06.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包含了您母親的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.12,0:12:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然姐姐已經死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.53,0:12:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但還是繼續保護著我愛羅少爺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.93,0:12:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜叉丸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.93,0:12:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.90,0:12:22.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.27,0:12:24.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧你及時阻止了我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.77,0:12:27.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.44,0:12:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我愛羅少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.88,0:12:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我身邊的那個最重要的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.80,0:12:59.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您能明白我的痛楚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.12,0:13:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有鐵的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.36,0:14:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,20
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.53,0:14:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,21
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.68,0:14:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木葉旋風
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.69,0:14:57.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡卡西 你打敗幾個了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.06,0:14:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,22個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.19,0:15:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看樣子又是我略勝一籌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.10,0:15:07.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才是第23個哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.53,0:15:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是 你比較厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.10,0:15:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就喜歡你這種坦率的個性
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.61,0:15:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣才是我永遠的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.71,0:15:16.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.27,0:15:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.59,0:15:34.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 夜叉丸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.60,0:15:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有事要拜託你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.73,0:15:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.20,0:15:41.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫我準備點創傷藥好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.75,0:15:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.38,0:15:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定很痛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.25,0:15:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是創傷藥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.75,0:15:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你收下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.75,0:16:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快滾吧 你這個怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.21,0:16:34.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走路當心點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.29,0:16:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.79,0:16:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.06,0:16:40.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.93,0:16:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快滾吧 你這個怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.93,0:16:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.13,0:16:45.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.13,0:16:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.31,0:16:58.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.68,0:17:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我愛羅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.95,0:17:02.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他已經死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.50,0:17:19.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.21,0:17:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果還是一點都不順利
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.19,0:17:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼只有我會變成那樣的怪物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.43,0:17:47.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底是什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.00,0:17:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以治療心裡創傷的藥就是愛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.17,0:17:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜叉丸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.26,0:18:16.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.46,0:18:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 為什麼是我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.86,0:18:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次都這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.29,0:18:52.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.36,0:18:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.36,0:19:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您真的好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.60,0:19:33.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛羅少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.58,0:19:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜叉丸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.86,0:19:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那種眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.33,0:20:00.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.89,0:20:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你剛才不是要逃跑的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.30,0:20:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.37,0:20:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對你而言 他們究竟是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.68,0:20:26.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們是我的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.62,0:20:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要再敢傷害他們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.99,0:20:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會幹掉你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.33,0:20:41.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來啊 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.40,0:20:44.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是說要幹掉我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.67,0:20:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.88,0:20:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.59,0:22:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道這個傢伙有多厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.03,0:22:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對他而言
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.77,0:22:54.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們幾個只是微不足道的蟲子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.70,0:22:57.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.50,0:23:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種湧上心頭的感覺是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.24,0:23:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不懂 雖然我不懂為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.84,0:23:07.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可即便要了我的命
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.08,0:23:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不想輸給這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.78,0:23:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.54,0:23:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光明與黑暗 我愛羅之名
